{"tid":2297484,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"社署女服務員街頭叫罵「黑警」 非法集結拒捕等罪成判囚10星期","createTime":"2020-11-23T10:06:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T14:43:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":294,"uniUserReply":99,"replies":[{"pid":"ef708ffd61b78441c5d1f0948a55c64ef9c4850b","tid":2297484,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:06:41.000Z","msg":"社署院舍女服務員去年11月晚上被指身穿拖鞋及街坊裝束，在街頭叫罵「黑警」，引起在場其他人叫囂。防暴男警欲強行扯開她的口罩時，她涉嫌推撞警員胸口。涉案女服務員被控非法集結、拒捕及違反蒙面法三罪，案件經審訊後，她今被裁定三罪罪成，判監10個星期。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官王證瑜裁決指，辯方質疑涉案警員未能指出如何制服被告，但王官認為現場情況涉及多人動作，情況混亂；至於警員未有記錄被告踢腳一事，王官指警員只是庭上回憶起更多而已，這沒有影響他的證供可靠性和可信性，認為警員作供誠實可靠。<br />\n<br />\n王官判刑指非法集結控罪嚴重，雖明白被告只是向警員出言辱罵，沒有作出其他行為，但需要將整個非法集結情況一同考慮，遂判處被告三罪共監禁10星期。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201123/ACBF2PGSZRCDVJRXU5O3BXJWK4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201123%2FACBF2PGSZRCDVJRXU5O3BXJWK4%2F&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUndHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=83b78f0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201123%2FACBF2PGSZRCDVJRXU5O3BXJWK4%2F&h=99965b65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201123/ACBF2PGSZRCDVJRXU5O3BXJWK4/</a>"},{"pid":"ad80c9087a8d8c17519f491dd3203f4baeec757e","tid":2297484,"uid":310867,"like":61,"dislike":3,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:07:14.000Z","msg":"死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c9b0999acc3dea978d84b1b2ca486a9d103887","tid":2297484,"uid":261937,"like":45,"dislike":3,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:07:54.000Z","msg":"事實陳述姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d931f48bf1c0f761c708d1543e275d4e8d35633","tid":2297484,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"s